<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GoHelp</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .sp-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .sp-header {
            background: #ff8c00;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .sp-section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .sp-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .sp-list {
            list-style-position: inside;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .sp-list li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .sp-requirements {
            counter-reset: requirements;
        }

        .sp-requirement-item {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .sp-requirement-item::before {
            counter-increment: requirements;
            content: counter(requirements) ".";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .sp-requirement-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline;
        }

        .sp-apply-button {
            display: block;
            background: #ff8c00;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            max-width: 300px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sp-apply-button:hover {
            background: #ff7300;
        }

        .sp-text {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sp-container {
                margin: 1rem;
                padding: 0.5rem;
            }
        }

        .sp-checkbox-group {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .sp-checkbox-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .sp-checkbox-item input[type="checkbox"] {
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            border: 2px solid #ff8c00;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .sp-checkbox-item label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            cursor: pointer;
        }



</style>
<body>

  <div class="sp-container hidden">
    <header class="sp-header">
        Want to Provide A Service...?
    </header>
  
    <section class="sp-section ">
        <h2 class="sp-title">Service Provider Requirements</h2>
        <p class="sp-text">Are you passionate about providing top-notch services? Join our team of trusted professionals! We are looking for reliable, skilled, and customer-focused individuals to deliver exceptional services in the following areas:</p>
        
        <ul class="sp-list">
            <li>Scrap Collecting</li>
            <li>Babysitting</li>
            <li>House Cleaning</li>
            <li>Handyman Services</li>
            <li>Water Tank Cleaning</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
  
    <section class="sp-section ">
        <h2 class="sp-title">Requirements:</h2>
        <div class="sp-requirements">
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Experience:</span> Prior experience in the relevant service area is preferred but not mandatory. Training can be provided for deserving candidates.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Professionalism:</span> A strong commitment to quality, reliability, and customer satisfaction.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Background Verification:</span> All applicants must undergo a background check for safety and trustworthiness.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Equipment:</span> Depending on the service, you may need to bring your tools or equipment.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Communication:</span> Ability to communicate effectively with clients and team members.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Punctuality:</span> Be punctual and adhere to the schedule agreed upon with clients.
            </div>
            <div class="sp-requirement-item">
                <span class="sp-requirement-title">Local Knowledge:</span> Familiarity with the service area is a plus.
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  
    <section class="sp-section">
        <h2 class="sp-title">Benefits of Joining Us:</h2>
        <ul class="sp-list">
            <li>Flexible working hours.</li>
            <li>Competitive pay and regular job assignments.</li>
            <li>Opportunity for growth and skill development.</li>
            <li>Be part of a trusted and growing business.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
  
    <p class="sp-text">If you meet the above requirements and are passionate about delivering excellent service, we'd love to hear from you!</p>
    
    <p class="sp-text">Apply Now:</p>
    <p class="sp-text">Click the button below to fill out our application form and start your journey with us.</p>
    
    <div class="sp-checkbox-group">
        <div class="sp-checkbox-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="consent" name="consent" required>
            <label for="consent">I consent to a background verification process</label>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-checkbox-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="terms" name="terms" required>
            <label for="terms">I agree to the terms and conditions of the platform.</label>
        </div>
    </div>
  
    <a href="#" class="sp-apply-button" id="accbtn">Become Service Provider</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    const acceptAgreementBtn = document.getElementById('accbtn');
    const agreeCheckbox = document.getElementById('consent');
    const agreeCheckbox2 = document.getElementById('terms');
    

    acceptAgreementBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (agreeCheckbox.checked && agreeCheckbox2.checked) {
            // Redirect to the target page
            window.location.href = "/serviceinput/";
        } else {
            alert("Please agree to the terms and conditions before proceeding.");
        }
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>